# =============================================================================
# INSTRUCTIONS FOR SETUP
# =============================================================================

# 1. REDIS SETUP:
#    - Local: Install Redis (brew install redis) and run redis-server
#    - Production: Use AWS ElastiCache or Redis Cloud
#    - Get connection details and update REDIS_* variables

# 2. PAYSTACK SETUP:
#    - Sign up at https://dashboard.paystack.com
#    - Get your test keys from Settings > API Keys & Webhooks
#    - For production, get live keys after account verification

# 3. AWS LAMBDA DEPLOYMENT:
#    - Deploy your Lambda function
#    - Get the Function URL or API Gateway endpoint
#    - Update API_BASE_URL with your endpoint


